OL,3,CLorry driver who rescued elderly
OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,FA lorry driver has been dubbed "Saint
OL,7,FChristopher" after he came to the
OL,8,Frescue of an elderly motorist left
OL,9,Fstranded when her tyres exploded on a
OL,10,Fmotorway.
OL,12,FPauline Sharp, 76, was driving along
OL,13,Fthe M18 in South Yorkshire after
OL,14,Fleaving her home in North Lincolnshire
OL,15,Fwhen she lost control of her car.
OL,17,FSuffolk trucker Christopher Dornelly,
OL,18,Fwho was in a lorry behind her,
OL,19,Fshepherded her to the side of the road
OL,20,Fand stayed with her until police and a
OL,21,Frecovery company arrived.
