OL,3,CLorry driver who rescued elderly
OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,FPauline said: "I think I met God that
OL,7,Fday. I really do. Something was saving
OL,8,Fme because, on paper, I shouldn't be
OL,9,Fhere.
OL,11,F"Everybody's calling him Saint
OL,12,FChristopher. He's one of the nicest
OL,13,Fpeople you'll ever meet - he's
OL,14,Fmessaged me every day to see if I'm
OL,15,Fall right."
OL,17,FPauline was on her way to Rotherham on
OL,18,F13 March when her car "lit up like a
OL,19,FChristmas tree" and started emitting
OL,20,Fsmoke.
