OL,3,CLorry driver who rescued elderly
OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,FShe said: "This lorry driver came up
OL,7,Fbehind me and was flashing me. He then
OL,8,Fovertook me, guided me to the side and
OL,9,Fpulled out in front to shield me from
OL,10,Ftraffic."
OL,12,FChristopher, who had just finished a
OL,13,Fdelivery to Selby, got out of his cab
OL,14,Fand put on a high-visibility jacket
OL,15,Fbefore warning traffic to move to one
OL,16,Fside.
