OL,3,CLorry driver who rescued elderly
OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,FPauline added: "He held my hand, took
OL,7,Fme out (of the car) and then walked me
OL,8,Fto the nearest barrier. Then we called
OL,9,Fthe police and the recovery people and
OL,10,Fhe stayed with me that whole time.
OL,12,F"It was terrifying and very scary, but
OL,13,Fhe calmed me down like you wouldn't
OL,14,Fbelieve. We started talking about his
OL,15,Ffamily and my family."
OL,17,FBefore he left, Pauline asked if she
OL,18,Fcould take Christopher's photograph to
OL,19,Fremember him.
