OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,FHer son later launched a Facebook
OL,7,Fcampaign to track him down and an
OL,8,Fonline fundraiser called "Buy
OL,9,FChristopher a pint".
OL,11,FThe post was liked 39,000 times, with
OL,12,Fmore than #1,300 donations to the
OL,13,Ffundraising page.
OL,15,FChristopher told ITV News: "Everything
OL,16,Fjust kicked off. It was overwhelming
OL,17,Fseeing all these kind messages coming
OL,18,Fin thick and fast.
OL,20,F"I was literally blown away."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
