OL,3,CLorry driver who rescued elderly
OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,FHe said he would donate some of the
OL,7,Fmoney to charity, adding: "I love
OL,8,Fhelping people - I feel it's a duty
OL,9,Ffor me. If I am on the road and I see
OL,10,Fsomeone that needs help, I make sure I
OL,11,Fcan help them. You don't know if it's
OL,12,Fa life or death situation."
OL,14,FAbby Holden, director at Anglia
OL,15,FFreight, where Christopher has worked
OL,16,Ffor seven years, said: "He is the very
OL,17,Fbest of the best."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
