OL,3,CLorry driver who rescued elderly
OL,4,Cmotorist dubbed 'St Christopher'
OL,6,F"He is pure joy to work with and
OL,7,Fbrings a real positivity in whatever
OL,8,Fhe does. He will do little gestures
OL,9,Fthroughout the day to make someone's
OL,10,Flife better."
OL,12,FPauline, who has been in touch with
OL,13,FChristopher almost daily, said: "Be
OL,14,Fmore Christopher... if there's more
OL,15,Fpeople like him then the world would
OL,16,Fbe a better place."
